title.narrative: Acre Social and Economic Inclusion and Sustainable Development Project - PROACRE

description.narrative: The objective of the Project is to contribute to the Borrower's efforts to promote social and economic inclusion of its rural and urban poor, including its poorest and most disadvantaged population living in isolated areas in the Borrower's territory.
